{
  "info": {
    "name": "Sistem Manajemen Kos - UTS PPLOS",
    "description": "Muhammad Rizky - 2410511049 - Kelas A\n\nMicroservices API untuk sistem manajemen kos.\n\n## Cara Penggunaan\n1. Jalankan semua service (Gateway :8000, Auth :8001, Property :8002, Booking :8003)\n2. Register akun owner dan tenant\n3. Login — token tersimpan otomatis ke variabel `access_token`\n4. Semua request yang butuh auth sudah pakai `{{access_token}}`\n\n## Variabel Koleksi\n- `base_url` — URL gateway (default: http://localhost:8000)\n- `access_token` — diisi otomatis saat login\n- `refresh_token` — diisi otomatis saat login\n- `property_id` — diisi otomatis saat create property\n- `room_id` — diisi otomatis saat create room\n- `booking_id` — diisi otomatis saat create booking",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "property_id",
